---

<section id="modulos" class="py-24 sm:py-32 bg-surface-50 dark:bg-dark-layer1">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-dark-text">
        +14 módulos, un solo sistema
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-surface-500 dark:text-dark-text2">
        Cada módulo resuelve un problema operativo real. No son features inventadas:
        son herramientas que yo necesitaba en mi día a día.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
      {modules.map((mod) => (
        <div class="group p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-dark-layer2 border border-surface-200 dark:border-dark-border hover:border-brand-300 dark:hover:border-brand-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-brand-50 dark:bg-brand-900/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 group-hover:bg-brand-100 dark:group-hover:bg-brand-900/30 transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d={icons[mod.icon]} />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-dark-text mb-1">{mod.name}</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-surface-400 dark:text-dark-text3 leading-relaxed">{mod.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm text-surface-400 dark:text-dark-text3">
        Y más: Blacklist, Conciliación, Backoffice, Notificaciones, Activity Log, Departamentos...
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
